These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, iced-tea, mirinda, cola
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, action, scientific, drama, thriller
There are 5 different nationalities: indonesian, canadian, brazilian, indian, dutch
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, goldfish, pony, frog
 1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching epic movies##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the brazilian##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the person drinking cola is between the canadian and the person watching thriller movies##2
12. the indian is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
13. the dutch is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | sprite        | soy-milk | cola     | iced-tea   | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | action      | drama | thriller   | epic    |
| Nationality   | indian  | canadian     | indonesian | brazilian | dutch  |
| Pet           | mouse | goldfish      | frog     | pony   | hedgehog     |

