.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, cooking, sudoku, traveling, magic-tricks
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, metal, reggae, house, ambient
There are 5 different nationalities: british, argentine, german, pakistani, colombian
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, van, train, snowmobile, bike
 1. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the argentine##1
 5. the person driving the van is between the british and the fan of ambient##2
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the german is the fan of house##1
 9. the german is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
10. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of metal##1
11. the german is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
12. the person driving the van is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | traveling | video-games | magic-tricks    | cooking  | sudoku    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | metal       | reggae      | hip-hop | house        |
| Nationality   | colombian   | argentine     | british    | pakistani  | german     |
| Transport     | train    | van | bike | snowmobile | tram |

