.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, chess, photography, baking, woodworking
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, drama, spy, epic
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, house, blues, hip-hop, punk
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, lacrosse, weightlifting, rugby
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of house##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person watching spy movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fan of punk##1
13. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching epic movies and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | fishing | woodworking     | photography   | chess   | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | sports | fantasy | spy | drama        |
| Music-Genre   | blues      | house      | hip-hop       | punk       | trance       |
| Sport         | sailing | rugby  | weightlifting    | parkour    | lacrosse        |

