.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: eggplant, cucumber, corn, grapefruit, radish
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, gardening, writing, sudoku, chess
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, classical, trance, hip-hop, punk
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, french, malaysian, australian, brazilian
 1. the french is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 4. the brazilian is between the fan of hip-hop and the person eating grapefruit##2
 5. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 6. the fan of punk is on the right of the malaysian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is the fan of classical##1
 9. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is the colombian##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
12. the colombian is on the right of the fan of trance##1
13. the fan of classical is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | radish  | corn     | grapefruit   | cucumber     | eggplant |
| Hobby         | chess | dancing    | writing  | sudoku | gardening   |
| Music-Genre   | classical        | electronic    | punk     | trance     | hip-hop    |
| Nationality   | french    | malaysian | australian | brazilian | colombian   |

