.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, soy-milk, water, fanta
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, pumpkin, zucchini, lime, lemon
The people have 5 different jobs:  entrepreneur, engineer, dressmaker, project-manager, accountant
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, basketball, lacrosse, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 2. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person eating nectarine##2
 5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the engineer##1
 8. the accountant is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
11. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the project-manager is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
13. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | water       | fanta       | 7up   | soy-milk      | tea    |
| Food       | lemon | lime        | nectarine       | zucchini       | pumpkin |
| Job        | accountant     | engineer        | project-manager | entrepreneur        | dressmaker  |
| Sport      | lacrosse | basketball | cricket      | snowboarding | skiing  |

