 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the pakistani##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is the spanish##1
 8. the thai is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the pakistani##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person who's sport is cricket##2
12. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the egyptian##1
13. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1

