 1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the fish is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the owner of the snake is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the german##2
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
 7. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
 8. the pakistani is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the chinese##1
10. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the australian##1
12. the owner of the cat is the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the owner of the snake is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Hobby         | baking   | dancing | writing  | chess | filmmaking |
