 5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the car is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
12. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | lemonade       | sprite    | fanta | water  | hot-chocolate        |
| Hobby       | collecting | rock-climbing | gardening  | camping | magic-tricks    |
| Sport       | soccer        | weightlifting   | cycling  | climbing   | swimming |
| Transport   | helicopter       | car      | airplane      | tram | bus  |

