The people have 5 different jobs:  software-developer, firefighter, dressmaker, accountant, freelancer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, action, mystery, disaster, horror
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, funk, soul, dubstep, folk
